    "The second stage constructs training samples with the selected orders and fine-tunes T5.",
    "They designed the following two strategies for selecting templates.",
    "• Dataset-level order (DLO) To choose the dataset-level orders, Hu et al. (2022) compute a score for each order on the training set.",
    "The Eq. 8 is from Hu et al. (2022).",
    "where S O i is the average entropy of all instances for the template order O i, T is the training set, E is the entropy function, y O i is the predicted quadruplet for the template order O i, and x is the input sentence."
  ],
